Thanks for all the love so far! Grain has already passed 13 000 downloads and we couldn t be more excited we ve got more features and updates coming your way so stay tuned! This is a quick small update that fixes a few of the crashes people have reported so far and adds a few features to the free version: Fixes color wheel thumb disappearing Fixes occasional crash when attempting to send feedback Adds loading indicator when purchasing subscription Now available in the free version: Cinematic Indie templates Curves tool Light leak LL1 bloom LB1 scaliness VHS1 Scratches All classic overlays More to come! If you have any feedback or questions don t hesitate to reach out at hello shopmoment.com. We d love to hear from you and help out however we can.
